headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Completes Acquisition of Woodruff Sawyer
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced it has completed the previously disclosed acquisition of San Francisco, California-based Woodruff Sawyer.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release And Conference Call Date
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE: AJG) will release its first quarter 2025 earnings after the market closes on Thursday, May 1, 2025. A printer-friendly format will be available on the company's website shortly thereafter.
